        <a href="/blog/aftercare-products" class="rounded-xl border border-ink-800 p-4 hover:border-accent-500/30 transition-all group"><p class="text-sm font-medium text-white group-hover:text-accent-300">Products that help</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">What to use &amp; skip</p></a>
        <a href="/blog/aftercare-issues" class="rounded-xl border border-ink-800 p-4 hover:border-accent-500/30 transition-all group"><p class="text-sm font-medium text-white group-hover:text-accent-300">Normal vs infection</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">Warning signs</p></a>
        <a href="/blog/aftercare-color-tattoo" class="rounded-xl border border-ink-800 p-4 hover:border-accent-500/30 transition-all group"><p class="text-sm font-medium text-white group-hover:text-accent-300">Color tattoo care</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">Protect vibrancy</p></a>
